ILT -- Image Layout Toolkit
---------------------------

The MNI Image Layout Toolkit is a set of Perl5 packages that can be
used to create images of geometry and volumes.  See the associated
documentation,  Documentation/ILT_tutorial.html for more information.

If ILT is not installed in the system directory, you will have to

      setenv PERLLIB dir_where_ILT_lives

